name: ArtfulAIchemist's Millie Bobby Brown v1
description:
Custom model of Millie Bobby Brown trained using Dreambooth on stable diffusion v1.5 as a base model.

Use the keyword 'mbb' to activate the model.

This model works with text2img as well as Img2Img. But for better pose I'd suggest to use other model like Protogen for text2image and then use Img2Img with this model. (Few of the Example images are created using this workflow).

I'm working on fixing this limitation. It'll be fixed with v2 of this model.
